OL,3,CInquiry to decide fate of destroyed
OL,4,CCrooked House pub set for summer
OL,6,FAn inquiry to hear the appeal and
OL,7,Fdecided the fate of the pub will open
OL,8,Fat 10.00am on Tuesday 23 July.
OL,10,FThe 258-year-old pub in Himley, near
OL,11,FDudley, was reduced to rubble
OL,12,Ffollowing a fire on 5 August 2023.
OL,14,FSix people have been with the fire,
OL,15,Fwhich is being treated as arson by
OL,16,Fpolice.
OL,18,Fsays the suspects currently remain on
OL,19,Fconditional police bail as the
OL,20,Finvestigation continues.
